    # arj "Aw. That's cute."
    arj "噢~ 真可爱。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:74
translate chinese e08s01_5d145c03:

    # mc "Since there's no roses growing around here, this one I named after you."
    mc "因为这附近没有玫瑰，所以我以你的名字给这朵花命名了。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:78
translate chinese e08s01_49a753e9:

    # mc "I have an app on my phone that identifies the names of different flowers and stuff."
    mc "我手机上有个程序，可以识别不同的花。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:79
translate chinese e08s01_a8a5e648:

    # mc "This one is called... don't kill me?"
    mc "这个叫...别杀我？"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:80
translate chinese e08s01_ff25483d:

    # arj "That's a weird name for a flower."
    arj "这花的名字真奇怪。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:81
translate chinese e08s01_022a4456:

    # mc "No. It's called Lydia."
    mc "不是。它叫莉迪亚。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:83
translate chinese e08s01_fcc7bb93:

    # arj "Lydia?"
    arj "莉迪亚？"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:84
translate chinese e08s01_a87a337b:

    # mc "Yep."
    mc "对头。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:85
translate chinese e08s01_e15a70a6:

    # arj "Really?"
    arj "你说真的？"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:87
translate chinese e08s01_56471a62:

    # mc "Yeah. I'm not even making that up. In French, it's called a fleur-de-Lydia."
    mc "对。不是我编的。在法语中，它被称为 "莉迪亚之花"。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:88
translate chinese e08s01_9e281d9a:

    # arj "Well, now I don't want it."
    arj "好吧，现在我不想要了。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:89
translate chinese e08s01_248c54d2:

    # mc "It's a good thing we don't live in France."
    mc "幸好我们不住在法国。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:91
translate chinese e08s01_7ac94059:

    # arj "I don't mind Lydia. Where do you think she's at now?"
    arj "我不介意莉迪亚。你觉得她现在在哪里？"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:92
translate chinese e08s01_537df6bc:

    # mc "Probably not on a farm, I can tell you that much."
    mc "我可以告诉你，可能不是在农场。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:93
translate chinese e08s01_af924cef:

    # arj "Hope you don't mind that I'm all dirty."
    arj "希望你不嫌弃我浑身脏兮兮的。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:95
translate chinese e08s01_abd46aeb:

    # mc "Of course I don't mind. Compared to the farm, you smell wonderful."
    mc "我当然不介意。和农场的味道比起来，你闻起来真香。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:96
translate chinese e08s01_61bf804b:

    # arj "Wow, such a compliment."
    arj "哇，太恭维我了。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:97
translate chinese e08s01_efb8a0fb:

    # mc "Well, I mean, we switched to using fresh cow dung instead of composting with eggshells."
    mc "嗯，我的意思是，我们改用新鲜的牛粪，而不是用蛋壳堆肥。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:99
translate chinese e08s01_df1a7216:

    # arj "It's more organic."
    arj "更有机。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:100
translate chinese e08s01_49c6ffe2:

    # mc "Oh, I know."
    mc "哦，我知道。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:101
translate chinese e08s01_88b407f3:

    # mc "Why is it that the most healthy stuff in nature always ends up smelling the worst?"
    mc "为什么自然界中最健康的东西总是闻起来最难闻？"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:103
translate chinese e08s01_63fd3f91:

    # arj "What do you mean?"
    arj "你指什么？"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:104
translate chinese e08s01_e3f3f4a4:

    # mc "You know, like kale."
    mc "你知道，就像甘蓝。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:105
translate chinese e08s01_43d9dcf2:

    # arj "Kale, huh? You just mean lettuce in general, right?"
    arj "甘蓝？你是指一般的生菜？"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:107
translate chinese e08s01_8a497fa4:

    # mc "I meant health foods. Anything green."
    mc "我是说健康食品。只要是绿色的都这样。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:108
translate chinese e08s01_ae0ca077:

    # arj "Well, it's mostly about preparation, isn't it? And what people are used to."
    arj "嗯，这主要跟制作过程有关吧？再说人们已经习惯了。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:109
translate chinese e08s01_54dc2f02:

    # arj "Some people never tasted raw milk, but for me, it tastes better coming straight from the source, than the supermarket sourced stuff."
    arj "有些人从来没尝过生牛奶，但对我来说，直接从源头来的牛奶比从超市买的味道更好。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:110
translate chinese e08s01_e7fc7dea:

    # mc "Yeah. I guess I never did grow out of my habits. I'm still used to that MegaBucks coffee."
    mc "嗯。像我就一直没改掉旧习惯。我还是习惯喝Mega超级咖啡。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:112
translate chinese e08s01_784b435e:

    # arj "Well, you're just proving my point. Nora's coffee wasn't just off the shelf stuff. It's artisanal."
    arj "嗯，你正好证明了我的观点。诺拉的咖啡可不是现成的，而是手工制作。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:113
translate chinese e08s01_7d3b437c:

    # arj "Anything can taste weird if you don't prepare it. And it's always nice to try new things as well."
    arj "如果不做准备，任何东西尝起来都会很怪。尝试新事物总是好的。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:114
translate chinese e08s01_f0ee82e7:

    # mc "I know. I never knew I would get used to this stuff."
    mc "我知道。我从来不知道自己会习惯这些东西。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:115
translate chinese e08s01_ccc384ee:

    # arj "It was a new beginning for both of us."
    arj "这对我们俩来说都是一个新的开始。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:117
translate chinese e08s01_d6f346ee:

    # mc "The only issue I have with it is that left in the barn, it could lead to an explosion."
    mc "唯一的问题是，把它放在仓房里，可能会导致爆炸。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:118
translate chinese e08s01_14e98a30:

    # arj "Explosion?"
    arj "爆炸？"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:119
translate chinese e08s01_a8989209:

    # mc "Yeah, if left in the barn, the nitrogen builds up and then the chemicals mix and match and it explodes."
    mc "对，如果留在谷仓里，氮气会积聚起来，然后化学物质混合在一起，就会爆炸。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:121
translate chinese e08s01_52910354:

    # arj "How would you know that?"
    arj "你怎么知道？"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:122
translate chinese e08s01_efc1c52a:

    # mc "Basic chemistry."
    mc "这是基础化学。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:123
translate chinese e08s01_442bfd1f:

    # mc "You know, the number one leading cause of deaths on a farm is caused by random barn explosions."
    mc "要知道，农场的头号死因就是由谷仓的随机爆炸引起的。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:125
translate chinese e08s01_52ae2508:

    # mc "That's why people don't compost."
    mc "所以人们才不使用堆肥。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:126
translate chinese e08s01_e5c1b983:

    # arj "I doubt it. How does a barn randomly explode?"
    arj "我不相信。谷仓怎么会随机爆炸呢？"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:127
translate chinese e08s01_b2959411:

    # mc "I don't know, that's why it's random."
    mc "我不知道，所以才叫它--随机爆炸啊。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:129
translate chinese e08s01_bbb798c9:

    # arj "Sure. Random."
    arj "呵。随机。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:130
translate chinese e08s01_0bd0a6ab:

    # mc "I'm serious. There's a reason why people use feces for fuel."
    mc "我是认真的。人们用粪便作为燃料是有原因的。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:131
translate chinese e08s01_2b11944b:

    # arj "What, so we need to be careful around poop?"
    arj "怎么，所以我们要小心大便吗？"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:133
translate chinese e08s01_a1f81024:

    # mc "How we store it, yes."
    mc "嗯，要小心储存它们。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:134
translate chinese e08s01_a71061bf:

    # mc "Hey, I'm not as big of a dummy as you think I am."
    mc "嘿，我没你想的那么傻。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:135
translate chinese e08s01_3153d55a:

    # mc "I mean, sure, I'm not a hotshot engineer like you, but a business degree has its uses."
    mc "当然，我在工程技术方面没你那么出色，但商科学位也有它的用处。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:137
translate chinese e08s01_f9eb84a5:

    # arj "Engineering is an applied science, whereas business is not."
    arj "工程学是一门应用科学，但商科不是。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:138
translate chinese e08s01_e9b2ee89:

    # arj "I don't think we need to advertise much for this job, anyway. The people come to us, not us to them."
    arj "反正，我觉得我们不需要为这个工作做很多推广。人们会来找我们，而不是我们找他们。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:140
translate chinese e08s01_de37dae0:

    # mc "You're living in the past. Stuck in the mud. Embrace the electronic age, baby."
    mc "你活在过去，陷在泥里了。拥抱电子时代吧，宝贝。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:141
translate chinese e08s01_d85b8b35:

    # mc "We should host some sort of farmer's market and get the word out, so people buy from us directly."
    mc "我们应该办个农贸市场，把消息传出去，这样大家就可以直接向我们购买。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:143
translate chinese e08s01_ffdf6ee4:

    # mc "Speaking of which, farmers."
    mc "说到这个，我们要谈谈，农民。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:144
translate chinese e08s01_acf23214:

    # arj "*Whispers* Plus I don't think you're a dummy. I picked you after all, didn't I?"
    arj "*低语* 再说，我不认为你是个笨蛋。我毕竟选了你，不是吗？"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:145
translate chinese e08s01_f39a644a:

    # mc "You made the right decision."
    mc "你的决定很正确。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:149
translate chinese e08s01_eb313e0a:

    # ac "Morning."
    ac "早啊。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:151
translate chinese e08s01_298da376:

    # mc "Hello, Mr. and Mrs. Cooper."
    mc "你好，库珀先生，库珀太太。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:153
translate chinese e08s01_b815bf08:

    # ac "Mrs. Cooper? That makes me sound so old. I would use your last name if I knew what it was."
    ac "库珀太太？听起来我好老啊。如果我知道你姓什么，我就跟你的姓。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:154
translate chinese e08s01_d34e1b7d:

    # mc "Young."
    mc "杨。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:155
translate chinese e08s01_26b7b119:

    # ac "That you are."
    ac "就姓杨了。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:157
translate chinese e08s01_99b2c393:

    # fc "How are things on the ginger farm?"
    fc "生姜农场的情况怎么样？"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:158
translate chinese e08s01_5c12820d:

    # arj "Oh, the usual."
    arj "哦，老样子。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:160
translate chinese e08s01_01dbbbb9:

    # ac "I like your hat."
    ac "我喜欢你的帽子。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:161
translate chinese e08s01_f915dcd4:

    # arj "[mcname] named it after me."
    arj "[mcname]以我的名字命名的。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:163
translate chinese e08s01_69a9d609:

    # ac "That's romantic. Frank never does any of that for me."
    ac "太浪漫了。弗兰克从来不为我做这些事。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:164
translate chinese e08s01_323a85e4:

    # fc "You never asked."
    fc "你从来没问过。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:165
translate chinese e08s01_f110cb6a:

    # fc "Really. She never asked."
    fc "真是这样。她从没问过。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:166
translate chinese e08s01_fd56f638:

    # ac "See what I live with?"
    ac "看到我和什么人一起生活了吗？"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:168
translate chinese e08s01_7f97070f:

    # arj "Did you folks need anything? Can I get you something to drink?"
    arj "你们需要什么吗？要不要喝点什么？"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:169
translate chinese e08s01_c12458fc:

    # fc "We won't be staying too long. I came over to ask if you had any more of that wire fencing."
    fc "我们不会待太久。我过来是想问问你，还有没有那种金属护栏。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:170
translate chinese e08s01_4718aa32:

    # fc "The usual guy I get it from is at some auction, and I want to finish setting this up before the Vinovella versus Minerva Bay game."
    fc "平时给我供货的那人在拍卖会上，我又想在维诺维拉对阵密涅瓦湾的比赛之前把这个布置好。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:171
translate chinese e08s01_d21ed967:

    # mc "Is that tomorrow?"
    mc "是明天吗？"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:172
translate chinese e08s01_6650e8dd:

    # fc "Yeah. Don't you read the newspaper?"
    fc "对。你不看报纸吗？"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:173
translate chinese e08s01_8b61fb97:

    # mc "Not much."
    mc "不怎么看。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:174
translate chinese e08s01_3d761780:

    # fc "I'm making cheese curds."
    fc "我在做奶酪凝乳。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:175
translate chinese e08s01_cfa5f012:

    # ac "Homemade cheese curds."
    ac "自制奶酪凝乳。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:177
translate chinese e08s01_72e95968:

    # mc "Do we have any more wire?"
    mc "咱们还有金属丝吗？"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:179
translate chinese e08s01_11d2150a:

    # arj "I think so."
    arj "应该还有。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:181
translate chinese e08s01_6f9f0827:

    # arj "Come with me, Frank."
    arj "跟我来，弗兰克。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:185
translate chinese e08s01_606bfc6f:

    # ac "So, what's a handsome, strapping fellow like you working on a farm like this?"
    ac "话说，像你这样英俊、魁梧的家伙在这样的农场工作，是为了什么呢？"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:187
translate chinese e08s01_baf6ab91:

    # mc "You know me. Homegrown and ready for work."
    mc "你了解我。土生土长，随时准备工作。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:189
translate chinese e08s01_993780f9:

    # ac "A young man like you ought to come over and do some work for me."
    ac "像你这样的年轻人，应该过来为我工作。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:190
translate chinese e08s01_88bb02ca:

    # ac "Maybe we can spend some time together."
    ac "也许我们可以处处看。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:194
translate chinese e08s01_ac6cb51e:

    # mc "If I wasn't naive, Mrs. Cooper, I would think you're hitting on me."
    mc "库珀太太，要不是我太天真，我会觉得你在勾引我。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:196
translate chinese e08s01_54b4df69:

    # ac "Is that what I was doing?"
    ac "你是这么理解的吗？"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:197
translate chinese e08s01_70416007:

    # ac "I was just talking."
    ac "我只是说说而已。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:199
translate chinese e08s01_c7a4a560:

    # mc "So was I."
    mc "我也是。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:201
translate chinese e08s01_9be82f9e:

    # ac "Give this to AmRose for me."
    ac "替我把这个交给爱洛丝。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:203
translate chinese e08s01_def0ad19:

    # mc "What is it?"
    mc "这是什么？"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:204
translate chinese e08s01_5582c124:

    # ac "What does it look like?"
    ac "它看起来像什么？"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:206
translate chinese e08s01_10b853df:

    # mc "No, I mean, which seeds are they?"
    mc "不，我是问，这是什么种子？"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:207
translate chinese e08s01_fb6316ef:

    # ac "It's a surprise! You'll have to wait until they grow out to see what they are."
    ac "这是个惊喜！你得等到它们长出来才知道是什么种子。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:209
translate chinese e08s01_83ff8f6d:

    # ac "For all you know, they're magic seeds that can grow money trees."
    ac "你要知道，它们是魔法种子，能长出摇钱树的那种。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:210
translate chinese e08s01_66df8773:

    # ac "Or they're just the regular money trees from China."
    ac "或者，它们只是来自中国的普通摇钱树。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:211
translate chinese e08s01_f899a236:

    # mc "Sounds like a real gamble, but I think I might know which one it is."
    mc "听起来真像是赌博，但我或许知道真相如何。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:213
translate chinese e08s01_c53e9436:

    # fc "I'll be heading off. Let's go."
    fc "该走了。动身吧。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:215
translate chinese e08s01_31929400:

    # fc "Good seeing you guys. Say hi to the little lady for me. Where is she, anyway?"
    fc "很高兴见到你们。替我向小宝贝儿问好。话说她在哪儿呢？"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:216
translate chinese e08s01_e9c220e4:

    # mc "Sleeping in the house."
    mc "在屋子里睡觉。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:217
translate chinese e08s01_a45f9705:

    # fc "I'll be sure to bring a treat for her next time I come over."
    fc "下次我来的时候一定给她带礼物。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:219
translate chinese e08s01_c121c6f2:

    # ac "Well, you know where to find me."
    ac "你知道去哪里找我。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:220
translate chinese e08s01_c85a0fd1:

    # ac "Bye, AmRose."
    ac "再见，爱洛丝。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:221
translate chinese e08s01_2a58ca71:

    # arj "See you later."
    arj "再见。"

# game/code/e08/e08s01.rpy:223
translate chinese e08s01_3629e496:

